<div class="box">    <h3 class="box__title">        Facility Level Information on GreenHouse gases Tool (FLIGHT)
          </h3>
      <div class="box__content">

  <p>FLIGHT provides maps, charts, and tables to quickly and easily filter GHG data in a variety of ways, including by facility, industry, location, or gas.</p><p><a href="https://ghgdata.epa.gov/flight"><strong>Click the map to launch the tool. &nbsp;</strong></a></p>

